      <ul>
        <li>Select a pickup location from the available nodes</li>
        <li>Choose a destination point different from the pickup</li>
        <li>Click "Calculate Path" to generate the optimal route</li>
        <li>View the calculated paths and performance metrics below</li>
      </ul>
